    "ministry_url": "https://curriculum.gov.bc.ca/curriculum/adst/12/robotics",
    "description": "Students develop advanced robotics skills including autonomous systems, AI integration, competition robotics, and capstone projects. This course emphasizes design thinking, programming, mechanical innovation, and real-world problem-solving in robotics.",
    "general_description": "Advanced robotics, autonomous systems, AI integration, competition and capstone projects.",
